<Author>fishoutofwater78
<Content>cant recommend highly enough a great hotel, only complaint i'd have is that some of the front rooms are subject to street noise, but it was only ever a minor irritation.staff were excellent, very friendly and accomodating.their apartment rooms were very comfortable, and extremely reasonable for what you get.great location too, handy for the metro and right beside montjuic, which is an absolute must-see. also the surrounding neighbourhoods are quiet and pleasant, very traditional.two thumbs up!p.s this also deserves a mention, out of 4 hotels i stayed in in barcelona, this hotel was the only one who's internet connection was both free (in other places the standard seems to be 22euro per 24h), and worked properly. 
